---
---
<section id="the-framework" class="the-framework">
  <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container-7 w-container">
    <div class="w-layout-vflex flex-block-8">
      <div class="text-block-7">The Framework</div>
      <h2 class="heading-4">6 Dimensions of Safety Maturity</h2>
      <p class="paragraph-6">
        Our framework benchmarks organisations across the areas <br />
        that drive real-world safety outcomes giving you a <br />
        complete, actionable picture.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-layout-vflex flex-block-24">
      <div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-10">
        <div class="div-block-24">
          <h5 class="heading-17">🔧  Vehicle Health</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-10">Inspection frequency, preventive maintenance maturity, and real-time fleet condition monitoring.</p>
          <div class="text-block-11">
            <span class="text-span-7">Industry median    </span>
            <span class="text-span-6">58/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-21">⚠ NHTSA estimates 20% of all road accidents are linked to poor vehicle maintenance</p>
        </div>
        <div class="div-block-25">
          <h5 class="heading-18">🎓  Training &amp; Culture</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-11">Safety training cadence, driver coaching programmes, and the depth of safety culture across your teams.</p>
          <div class="text-block-12">
            <span class="text-span-7">Industry median    </span>
            <span class="text-span-6">55/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-22">⚠ Untrained drivers are significantly more likely to be involved in preventable incidents</p>
        </div>
        <div class="div-block-26">
          <h5 class="heading-19">📊  Reporting &amp; Data</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-12">Data collection quality, reporting cadence, and the extent to which analytics drives safety decisions.</p>
          <div class="text-block-13">
            <span class="text-span-7">Industry median    </span>
            <span class="text-span-6">49/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-24">⚠ Organisations without structured data reporting fail to identify most near-miss events</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-layout-hflex flex-block-9">
        <div class="div-block-21">
          <h5 class="heading-14">🚗  Driver Behaviour</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-7">Speeding, harsh braking, distracted driving patterns and overall behind-the-wheel conduct.</p>
          <div class="text-block-10">
            <span class="text-span-7">Industry median    </span>
            <span class="text-span-6">72/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-26">✓ Above industry average - maintain regular driver coaching to hold this lead</p>
        </div>
        <div class="div-block-22">
          <h5 class="heading-15">⚠️  Incident Response</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-8">How effectively your organisation detects, reports, investigates, and closes safety incidents.</p>
          <div class="text-block-8">
            <span class="text-span-9">Industry median</span>
            <span class="text-span-6">61/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-25">⚠ Incidents without structured closure processes are far more likely to repeat</p>
        </div>
        <div class="div-block-23">
          <h5 class="heading-16">📋  Compliance Management</h5>
          <p class="paragraph-9">Licence renewals, certification tracking, regulatory adherence, and audit <br />readiness.</p>
          <div class="text-block-9">
            <span class="text-span-8">Industry median</span>
            <span class="text-span-6">68/100</span>
          </div>
          <p class="paragraph-27">⚠ Licence and certification lapses are among the leading triggers for fleet regulatory fines</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
